box": [240.7, 1281.7, 611.8, 1302.6]}, {"text": "During December 2008, the Company’s second fiscal quarter, the Company announced a restructuring plan to", "bbox": [166.8, 1320.4, 1073.3, 1341.2]}, {"text": "realign its cost structure as a result of a softer demand environment. This plan was completed during the Company’s third", "bbox": [125.0, 1345.4, 1073.3, 1366.3]}, {"text": "and fourth fiscal quarters of 2009. This resulted in the closure of one of the Company’s hard drive manufacturing facilities", "bbox": [125.0, 1370.4, 1073.3, 1391.2]}, {"text": "in Thailand, the disposal of its media substrate manufacturing facility in Sarawak, Malaysia, and headcount reductions", "bbox": [125.0, 1395.4, 1073.3, 1416.2]}, {"text": "throughout the world of approximately 3,300 people. During the fourth fiscal quarter, the Company sold its media", "bbox": [125.0, 1420.5, 1073.4, 1441.3]}, {"text": "substrate manufacturing facility, and related assets, in Sarawak, Malaysia for net proceeds of approximately $29 million,", "bbox": [125.0, 1445.4, 1072.9, 1466.2]}, {"text": "77", "bbox": [588.8, 1495.5, 609.7, 1516.3]}, {"text": "WESTERN DIGITAL CORPORATION", "bbox": [408.2, 134.8, 790.4, 155.6]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS — (Continued)", "bbox": [221.9, 172.3, 976.3, 193.2]}]}